# ReadMe

## Requirements

* [ocicl](https://github.com/ocicl/ocicl)
* [peru](https://github.com/buildinspace/peru)
* [just](https://github.com/casey/just)
* [sbcl](https://sbcl.org/)


## Dependencies

### Installation

This will install current dependencies of the project to their saved versions.

```sh
just install-deps
```

### Update dependencies 

This will update all dependencies and install them.

```sh
just update-deps
```

## Running as interpreted script

The file `{{ project }}-i` will run the cli module's main function.


## Building

The `build` command will create a binary named `{{ project }}` that will have the script dumped for fast execution.
